node.text:
During my isolation it was tough not being able to gym, but had to find the motivation to get some type of sweat in so I came up with a few workouts, so here’s a good one! try this if you’re stuck in the house or if your gym isn’t open!

-30 sec jump rope
-30 sec in and out squat jumps
-30 sec RDL to squat
-30 sec lunge up jumps
-30 sec alt side plank twists

Wearing my own @get_tighterr sweat belt to make me feel tight and to sweat a little extra durning my HIIT workouts 😁 you can pre order yours with the link in my bio! 
Sizes S-XXL (true to size)
I’m wearing a medium

node.text:
You guys I’m OBSESSED with this dessert..
Literally every night I make this and eat it after dinner.
Here’s my little tutorial on how I make it!
- 3 egg whites
- 1 scoop @iammotiv8 dessert protein
- 2 TBS coca powder
- 1/2 cup plain pumpkin.
- dash baking powder 
Mix all together and bake on parchment paper for 15-20 min on 350 degrees.
Brownie by it’s self is around d 200 cal and it’s a pretty big size!

If you try this recipe let me know!!
————-
If you want to try this protein use my code MOTIV8JESSICA for free shipping!
This is cookie dough protein, their blueberry is also amazingggg.
